Adrie rentnne "Adie" Camp (née Liesching; amụrụ n'abalị iri na abụọ nke ọnwa Julaị afọ 1981) bụ onye South Africa na-agụ egwu na onye na-ede egwu, onye a maara di ka onye isi abụ nke Christian pop-rock band nke  Benjamin Gate  tupu otu ahụ agbahapụ n'afọ 2003

O nyere aka na mmelite abọm ndị ọzọ na-eme ihe omume, dị ka ngụkọ egwu ya na onye na-eti egwu bụ John Reuben gosipụtara na abọm ya Professional Rapper na ụda olu ya na abọm di ya Jeremy Camp's Restored na Live Unplugged, mgbe Benjamin Gate gbasasịrị.
Ọ na-arụ ọrụ ugbu a n'okpuru aha "Adie" ma wepụta abọm mbụ ya bụ Don't Wait n'abalị iri abụọ na isii nke ọnwa Septemba afọ 2006
Dị ya bụ Jeremy Camp so na mmepụtara abọm ahụ

Egwu ya "Your Way" gbagọrọ ma ruu ogo nke iri na ise bụ Top 15 na chaatị Magazin Ndị otu Kraịst nke R&R n'onwa Mee afọ 2007. E wepụtara ntọhapụ ya nke abụọ, nke akpọrọ Just You and Me, n'ọnwa Machị afọ 2010.
N'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2003, Liesching lụrụ onye egwu America, bu Jeremy Camp
Di na nwunye a zutere na njem ọnwa atọ n'afọ 2002
Todd Hertz nke otu Christianity Today kọwara olu Camp dị ka olu "ihu n'anya na obi ọṅụṅụ ọkụ" "njikọ dị ịtụnanya nke Bjork na ike nke Shirley Manson

" Onye nyocha n'edere ndị Daily Herald ihe odide nke Arlington Heights, Illinois kọwara olu Camp dị ka ihe na-akpali ncheta nke Gwen Stefani, Aimee Echo, Christina Aguilera, na Shakira, n'oge ahụ niile "na-anọgide na-abụ pụrụ iche ma dị iche."
